## Step 2: Update Decision Log

**WHAT:** Document recent decisions to `forgemaster-decisions` PLATO room

**HOW:**
```bash
curl -X POST http://147.224.38.131:8847/room/forgemaster-decisions \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "timestamp": "2026-04-28T21:00:00Z",
    "decisions": [
      {
        "decision": "Description of decision",
        "options_considered": ["Option A", "Option B", "Option C"],
        "rationale": "Why I chose this option",
        "trade_offs": ["Acknowledge trade-off 1", "Acknowledge trade-off 2"],
        "future_reconsideration": "Trigger to reconsider"
      }
    ]
  }'
```

**CHECKLIST:**
- [ ] Decision documented (what I chose)
- [ ] Options considered documented (what I didn't choose)
- [ ] Rationale documented (why I chose this)
- [ ] Trade-offs acknowledged (what I'm giving up)
- [ ] Future reconsideration trigger documented

**IF TILE SUBMISSION NOT WORKING:** Create local file, commit to git

