## Step 5: Update Project Rooms

**WHAT:** Update project-specific PLATO rooms for each active project

**EXAMPLE: Marine GPU Edge**
```bash
curl -X POST http://147.224.38.131:8847/room/forgemaster-marine-gpu-edge \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
